reviews.review_text: A Nice Surprise It's been a long time since I heard this one.  I saw this show in A2  (that was the first time I'd seen the band in six years).  It's a pleasant surprise to hear it again.  Beautiful.  Just be patient cause halfway thru NMB, the boys really got things rolling.  In Peggy-O, you'll have a tear in your eye remembering how lovely their work could be.
